    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Meet Bumble...<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1863120/extras/e8aecfb73ec97f53ae1d037f5703ddc4.poster.avif?t=1771820809\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1863120/extras/e8aecfb73ec97f53ae1d037f5703ddc4.webm?t=1771820809\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1863120/extras/e8aecfb73ec97f53ae1d037f5703ddc4.mp4?t=1771820809\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >He's a bee...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A very angry bee!<br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1863120/extras/dd801abf939dc8da3bc39893ee90ca9e.poster.avif?t=1771820809\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1863120/extras/dd801abf939dc8da3bc39893ee90ca9e.webm?t=1771820809\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1863120/extras/dd801abf939dc8da3bc39893ee90ca9e.mp4?t=1771820809\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You see, he hates the smell of flowers...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help him on his goal to eat them all!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1863120/extras/804ac5736548015f9a97d3895d2da159.poster.avif?t=1771820809\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1863120/extras/804ac5736548015f9a97d3895d2da159.webm?t=1771820809\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1863120/extras/804ac5736548015f9a97d3895d2da159.mp4?t=1771820809\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Description:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this fast-paced, roguelike, arcade game, you are the bad guy. Navigate your way through many unfair matchups against the toughest ecosystem safeguards!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Weave Through:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Worm Wardens</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1863120/extras/509ee647c8dc9cee8f5771856d16294b.poster.avif?t=1771820809\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1863120/extras/509ee647c8dc9cee8f5771856d16294b.webm?t=1771820809\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1863120/extras/509ee647c8dc9cee8f5771856d16294b.mp4?t=1771820809\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Butterfly Bouncers</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1863120/extras/1fcd45f0874fee72337a9a68c8d59d38.poster.avif?t=1771820809\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1863120/extras/1fcd45f0874fee72337a9a68c8d59d38.webm?t=1771820809\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1863120/extras/1fcd45f0874fee72337a9a68c8d59d38.mp4?t=1771820809\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bird Barriers</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1863120/extras/dde7cc0219ae5a9a7b8cec24804c7a6f.poster.avif?t=1771820809\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1863120/extras/dde7cc0219ae5a9a7b8cec24804c7a6f.webm?t=1771820809\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1863120/extras/dde7cc0219ae5a9a7b8cec24804c7a6f.mp4?t=1771820809\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And Duel Defenders</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1863120/extras/5d1881065851d7117e1c6eaf62db5d6c.poster.avif?t=1771820809\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1863120/extras/5d1881065851d7117e1c6eaf62db5d6c.webm?t=1771820809\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1863120/extras/5d1881065851d7117e1c6eaf62db5d6c.mp4?t=1771820809\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>-Randomized Runs</strong> <br>Each wave is randomly ordered, with random enemy start points; no run will be the same! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1863120/extras/4d6bf06d4abc42c161f14e99d7741846.poster.avif?t=1771820809\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1863120/extras/4d6bf06d4abc42c161f14e99d7741846.webm?t=1771820809\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1863120/extras/4d6bf06d4abc42c161f14e99d7741846.mp4?t=1771820809\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><br>-Pickup'n'Play</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kamakazzzbee is easy to understand and start playing, with its minimalistic design, and its singular multifunctional dash ability.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1863120/extras/31461a2a84a88df060e5121919a67d4b.poster.avif?t=1771820809\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1863120/extras/31461a2a84a88df060e5121919a67d4b.webm?t=1771820809\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1863120/extras/31461a2a84a88df060e5121919a67d4b.mp4?t=1771820809\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><br>-Difficulty</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You Will Die. A Ton. Like a Lot. Like you probably won't last a minute <i>(its pretty hard)</i>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1863120/extras/ab479dba889eaddcb91f678ca9625120.avif?t=1771820809\" width=400 height=224 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><br>-Addicting Gameplay</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hard hooking gameplay that only ends with you buying a new controller!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1863120/extras/5952fb184e027cf61de99d92d880878c.avif?t=1771820809\" width=400 height=224 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EAT ALL FLOWERS!</h2>",
